{
  "stem": "17720.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 117.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it my activity, musical activity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he introduced to me scales, how I am able to produce actually diatonic scale and some of the instrument, the xylophone as well as the recorder.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this somewhat developed my techniques of playing and increase my musical knowledge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I also, on the time, seems to me that received my first unformal lesson of music how to write and how to read these little scales that were introduced to me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember the living conditions?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other conditions-- basically, the mood of the people was very depress.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All this visiting and festive dresses disappear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that my father, he was not working anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was spending--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was, before that, teaching mathematics in the universities, and physics.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- I think that what they basically were doing were arranging their activities in the synagogue and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] trying to develop some kind of survival.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How they arranged the survival and bringing the food, this was little but unknown terrain for me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But food was always at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had all the time what to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And basically, we were kept in-- I was kept in good health.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Formerly, I think that I was officially allowed to leave this area, regarding the laws of the government.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the factum, I was not allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because any Jewish person that was living there was subject to some very severe, very ferocious persecution, being beaten or risk to be killed, even.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If they left the area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the really official persecutions came little bit later on after that we left the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And obviously, the, the government establish much more their character as a fascistic government.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
